show grants for 'halB';
Grants for halB@%
GRANT SUPER ON *.* TO 'halB'
GRANT `role_g3`@`%`,`role_g2`@`%`,`role_g1`@`%` TO `halB`@`%`
select current_role();
+-------------------------------------------+
| current_role()                            |
+-------------------------------------------+
| `role_g3`@`%`,`role_g2`@`%`,`role_g1`@`%` |
+-------------------------------------------+
